=> API Design Documentation

1. Base URL:

http://localhost:8000


2. Endpoints:

## POST /add_calendar
Request:
{
    "user_id": "u1",
    "date": "2026-02-21",
    "busy_slots": [
        {"start": "10:00", "end": "11:00"}
    ]
}

Response:
{
    "status": "calendar stored"
}


## POST /add_preference
Request:
{
    "user_id": "u1",
    "preference_text": "I prefer morning meetings"
}
Response:
{
    "status": "preference stored"
}


## POST /schedule
Request:
{
    "user_id": "u1",
    "duration_minutes": 30
}
Response:
{
    "suggestions": [
        {"start": "09:00", "end": "09:30"}
    ]
}
